599065754705604608:::Fri May 15 04:16:20 +0000 2015:::"I'm more focussed on winning than getting my personality out there on game day." -AS:::None
599065614536216576:::Fri May 15 04:15:47 +0000 2015:::"I'm concentrating on what we're doing during the game and I let a little bit of steam out at the end of the game." -AS:::None
599065415080259585:::Fri May 15 04:14:59 +0000 2015:::"Lecca is dangerous all over the ground. He knows how to find the ball and he can kick goals. He's really important for us." -AS:::None
599065197186187265:::Fri May 15 04:14:07 +0000 2015:::"To win away from home last week was great
column2: and that is part of our development." -AS:::None

column1: 599065062666477568:::Fri May 15 04:13:35 +0000 2015:::"Our path is about development and education. Our boys are aware they're the front line of the club and are accountable." -AS:::None
599064869464211456:::Fri May 15 04:12:49 +0000 2015:::"GCS are going to be a really good side. I just hope that's not this week." -AS:::None
599064755052019714:::Fri May 15 04:12:22 +0000 2015:::"The ladder hasn't settled yet. You only have to be off a little bit to miss out. The competition is so close and it's showing." -AS:::None
599064571496763392:::Fri May 15 04:11:38 +0000 2015:::"Ask me how our season is going in a month's time. We'll know a lot more where we sit in the league." -AS:::None
599064429267800064:::Fri May 15 04:11:04 +0000 2015:::"To play in front of our home crowd
column2: supporters and fans is always special." -AS:::None

column1: 599064295045902336:::Fri May 15 04:10:32 +0000 2015:::"Sharrod is doing his job on and off the ball. We're really pleased with how he's playing." -AS:::None
599064166503026689:::Fri May 15 04:10:02 +0000 2015:::"He's still developing. He's 20 years old and he'll get his opportunity and he'll take it with both hands when he gets it." -AS:::None
599063986399682561:::Fri May 15 04:09:19 +0000 2015:::"Colledge needs another run at East Perth to get another full game. He was the emergency last week." -AS:::None
599063813560762368:::Fri May 15 04:08:37 +0000 2015:::"Matty Rosa twinged his hammy
column2: so unfortunately he'll miss a few more weeks." -AS:::None

column1: 599063676121796608:::Fri May 15 04:08:05 +0000 2015:::"Our attitude to the contest and our engagement with the game in the last month has been good. We need that again this week." -AS:::None
599063516172038144:::Fri May 15 04:07:26 +0000 2015:::"It's hard to predict what's going to happen with the weather
column2: we'll only really know when we're an hour out." -AS:::None
